@host = {{host}}
@token = {{token}}
@documentCollectionId = {{documentCollectionId}}
@documentId = {{documentId}}

### Vincular documento ya existente (`document_registry`) a esta colección
# Devuelve: 201 y el objeto de enlace; 409 si `duplicate_document_link`.

POST {{host}}/api/v1/document-collections/{{documentCollectionId}}/documents/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "document_id": {{documentId}}
}

###

### Vincular otro numeric id (ajústalo contra tu base)

POST {{host}}/api/v1/document-collections/{{documentCollectionId}}/documents/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "document_id": 999999
}

###

### Validación — document_id ilegal (≤0)

POST {{host}}/api/v1/document-collections/{{documentCollectionId}}/documents/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "document_id": 0
}

###

### Cuerpo vacío (falta `document_id`)

POST {{host}}/api/v1/document-collections/{{documentCollectionId}}/documents/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}
